_source.headline: Showcase

_source.body:
In this report, Xtract Research shows that GNC's credit agreement contains the same "trap-door" provision that allowed J. Crew to boost its investment capacity for investments in unrestricted subsidiaries. With the "trap-door" investment capacity boost, GNC's credit agreement provides significant investment capacity for investment in unrestricted subsidiaries and secured debt issuance capacity at foreign subsidiaries.
